I think we need more meaning.

14:55.394 --> 15:01.868 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: What kind of
context are
you able to get when you are
walking vs. when

15:01.901 --> 15:04.337 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
