and trains?

15:04.370 --> 15:09.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: Walking has shown
me that the
boundaries between stories are
permeable,

15:09.142 --> 15:14.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in that one story bleeds into
another, because
