15:59.358 --> 16:01.894 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And we were very afraid of
hypothermia.

16:01.928 --> 16:06.365 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Salopek and
three walking
partners found this "Spotlight".
One man set

16:06.399 --> 16:09.569 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
his gloves alight to start a
fire and stay
