16:09.602 --> 16:15.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: On a November
night a year ago,
this was heaven. This was better
than a five-star

16:15.675 --> 16:17.510 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
hotel.

16:17.543 --> 16:21.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Then he waited
