ancient eruptions.

16:35.828 --> 16:40.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL SALOPEK: When our
ancestors, the first
people who walked out of Africa,
passed through

16:40.833 --> 16:47.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this region, their big obstacles
were glaciers
and big animals that would eat
them or droughts

16:47.340 --> 16:53.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
