17:14.133 --> 17:15.935 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and beyond.

17:15.968 --> 17:19.672 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: This doesn't look
like much,
but this ruin on the high
plateau of Southern

17:19.705 --> 17:25.311 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Georgia is the beginning of
phase two of the
Out of Eden Walk. So, this is
the gateway

17:25.344 --> 17:29.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
