the Caucasus, going on the old
silk roads

17:29.181 --> 17:31.017 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to China.

17:31.050 --> 17:35.655 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So at
