of civilization.

18:04.116 --> 18:08.854 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: We came around the
corner of
this mountain river and here was
this village

18:08.888 --> 18:10.723 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
