existed.

18:10.756 --> 18:14.427 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
The first reaction was
curiosity. When I finally
told him, well, actually, I have
hiked all

18:14.460 --> 18:18.364 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
