18:57.303 --> 19:01.007 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
What is the reaction of most of
the people
you bump into when you tell them
what he's

19:01.040 --> 19:02.808 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
