(LAUGHTER)

19:23.562 --> 19:25.264 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Yes.

19:25.297 --> 19:28.934 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DIMA BIT-SULEIMAN: Like, why is
