19:53.759 --> 19:55.594 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

19:55.628 --> 20:00.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SALOPEK: The walk has
opened up the vista
to me in both space and time,
where I can

20:00.699 --> 20:04.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
see the connections between all
